nodes.text: A Human female individual worked as a journalist on the galactic capital world of Coruscant in 33 BBY. Supreme Chancellor Finis Valorum found her attractive. After a session of the Galactic Senate that saw the ratification of a resolution subjecting free trade routes to Republic taxation, the female was one of many journalists who surrounded the Chancellor to field questions. Their concerns were addressed by Valorum's Staff Aide, Sei Taria.
